<item>
            <title>[HIVE-15035] Clean up Hive licenses for binary distribution</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-15035</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hive&apos;s current LICENSE file contains information not needed for the source distribution.  For the binary distribution we are missing many license files as a number of jars included in Hive come with various licenses.  This all needs cleaned up.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13014524">HIVE-15035</key>
            <summary>Clean up Hive licenses for binary distribution</summary>
