&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Right now this is blocking 2.3 release. (I believe it will block 2.2 as well as it makes rat check broken).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Shall we revert this patch or do something else? Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15971854" author="alangates" created="Mon, 17 Apr 2017 23:58:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;All related JIRAs closed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15979196" author="pxiong" created="Fri, 21 Apr 2017 18:35:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=gates&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;gates&quot;&gt;gates&lt;/a&gt;, i tried master and 2.3 just now. However ,the same problem still remains...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15979204" author="alangates" created="Fri, 21 Apr 2017 18:40:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ah, I forgot to modify RAT to tell it not to pay attention to these.  I&apos;ll open a separate issue for that.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15979209" author="alangates" created="Fri, 21 Apr 2017 18:43:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Created &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-16504&quot; title=&quot;Addition of binary licenses broke rat check&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HIVE-16504&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HIVE-16504&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; to deal with the rat issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
